# Personal context — never commit account names, character names, or build secrets
CLAUDE.local.md
user/*.md
!user/README.md
!user/_template.md

# Local MCP config — holds per-user paths, email and generated crypto keys. Never commit.
# The committed template is .mcp.json.canonical (with placeholders); the setup check
# turns it into a working .mcp.json on first run.
.mcp.json
!.mcp.json.canonical

# Local Claude Code state
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/projects/

